{
  "text": "Indicators and items that are meaningful have been identified according to the medical practice in health assessment of elderly [CITATION_1] and encoded in our declarative framework as logic facts. A reduced list of indicators evaluated by the system is provided in Table 5 while items are grouped according to the class they belong to, as described later in this section.",
